Feature: View a beer

  In order to see details on a beer
  As an API client
  I want to be able to view a beer

  Background:
    Given the following breweries exist:
      | id | name  |
      | 1  | Abita |
    And the following beer styles exist:
      | id | name                           | description      |
      | 1  | Fruit / Vegetable Beer         | Fruity and stuff |

  Scenario: Viewing a beer
    Given the following beer exists:
      | id | user | brewery     | beer_style                   | name               | description | abv | created_at | updated_at |
      | 1  |      | name: Abita | name: Fruit / Vegetable Beer | Strawberry Harvest | Southern.   | 4.2 | 2010-01-01 | 2010-02-02 |
    When I send an API GET request to /v1/beers/1.json
    Then I should receive a 200 response
    And I should see the following JSON response:
      """
        { "id"          : 1,
          "name"        : "Strawberry Harvest",
          "description" : "Southern.",
          "abv"         : 4.2,
          "created_at"  : "2010-01-01T00:00:00Z",
          "updated_at"  : "2010-02-02T00:00:00Z",
          "brewery"     : {
            "id"   : 1,
            "name" : "Abita"
          },
          "beer_style" : {
            "id"   : 1,
            "name" : "Fruit / Vegetable Beer"
          }
        }
      """

